with your W's.

16:16.534 --> 16:19.811
I do.
I-I-I really struggle with that.

16:21.039 --> 16:24.590
Look, Mr. Higgins, I'm
sure you can see the --
the humor in all of this.

16:24.592 --> 16:26.876
