There is more.

16:26.878 --> 16:28.820
No.
"Henry is playing the guitar

16:28.822 --> 16:30.880
and making
that bleeping face,

16:30.882 --> 16:34.367
and I want to rip it off
and shove it up his bleep."

16:35.144 --> 16:36.310
Okay, you know what?

16:36.312 --> 16:37.811
I think we can say "ass,"
alright?

16:37.813 --> 16:39.146
It's an animal,
and it was heavily featured

16:39.148 --> 16:41.332
in the Christmas story,
if I recall.

16:41.334 --> 16:44.243
She didn't write "ass."
I gathered that.

16:44.245 --> 16:48.564
