16:48.566 --> 16:50.566
Wow, you really don't like
my guitar face.

16:50.568 --> 16:52.568
Oh, please do not be
so sensitive.

16:52.570 --> 16:54.762
Your texting face
isn't so great, either.

16:56.165 --> 16:59.500
Henry, that is hurtful.
I'm a lady.

16:59.502 --> 17:01.185
Yeah, well.
You talk like a sailor.

17:01.187 --> 17:02.428
You got to
filter yourself.

17:02.430 --> 17:04.689
Oh, w--
I have to filter myself?

17:04.691 --> 17:06.673
Are you kidding me?
You don't filter yourself.

17:06.675 --> 17:10.010
Yeah, I do.
I filter myself all the time.

17:10.012 --> 17:12.346
Morning, noon,
especially right now.

17:12.348 --> 17:14.440
Okay, well, some of us
aren't fake.

17:14.442 --> 17:15.366
This is who I am.

17:15.368 --> 17:17.260
Why should I change
for the kids?

17:17.262 --> 17:19.445
I was here first.
Very mature.

17:19.447 --> 17:20.596
You're very mature.

17:20.598 --> 17:23.282
Look, no one's saying
you can't be you,

17:23.284 --> 17:25.025
